Package nachos.filesys

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    File
    File provide some basic IO operations.
    FileStat  
    FilesysKernel
    A kernel with file system support.
    FilesysProcess
    FilesysProcess is used to handle syscall and exception through some callback methods.
    Folder
    Folder is a special type of file used to implement hierarchical filesystem.
    FreeList
    FreeList is a single special file used to manage free space of the filesystem.
    INode
    INode contains detail information about a file.
    RealFileSystem
    RealFileSystem provide necessary methods for filesystem syscall.
